Package: edge1d
Title: Performs multi-scale edge detection on 1D data.
Version: 0.1
Author: Steve Lianoglou
Maintainer: Steve Lianoglou <slianoglou@gmail.com>
Description: Detects edges in 1D space via canny edge detector.
  .
  This code is adapted from the MATLAB edge_detector_1d written
  by the CISMM group at UNC. See URLs for reference.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 2.13.0), Rcpp (>= 0.9.7)
Imports: Rcpp, methods
Suggests: testthat (>= 0.5)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: http://lianos.github.com/edge1d/,
     http://cismm.cs.unc.edu/resources/tutorials/edge-detector-1d-tutorial/
Repository: CRAN
